programme.title: A Timeless Christmas
programme.desc: A man travels from 1903 to 2020, where he meets a tour guide at his historic mansion and gets to experience a 21st century Christmas.

programme.title: A Season for Family
programme.desc: Maddys adopted son, Wesley, has just one wish for Christmas -- to meet his brother, Cody, who was adopted into a different family. Circumstances soon bring the two siblings together while sparks fly between their respective parents.

programme.title: Deliver by Christmas
programme.desc: Bakery owner Molly meets Josh, a newcomer in town, but is also enchanted by a mysterious client whom shes never met in person. A special wish to be delivered by Christmas could help determine who will win Mollys heart.

programme.title: Moms Christmas Boyfriend
programme.desc: A precocious 10-year-old girl makes a Christmas wish for her adoptive mother to find true love.

programme.title: Creating Christmas
programme.desc: Aspiring illustrator Harper collaborates with demanding author Caleb. When he insists on working through Christmas in a quaint town, she must use the holiday celebrations to help break his writers block.

programme.title: Three Wise Men and a Baby
programme.desc: Three brothers get the surprise of their lives when they are forced to work together and care for a baby over the holidays.

programme.title: Single and Ready to Jingle
programme.desc: A womans vacation plans go disastrously wrong when she mistakenly winds up in St. John, Alaska, during Christmastime. However, things take a turn for the better when she meets a local man who sweeps her off her feet.

programme.title: Hollywood on Set

programme.desc: Features behind-the-scenes footage from movie sets and discussions with the cast and crew about the details of each film.

programme.title: Sister Swap: A Hometown Holiday
programme.desc: Two sisters find a new sense of purpose and discover what they both truly need in life during the holidays.

programme.title: Meet Me at the Christmas Train Parade
programme.desc: When Charlottes son Benny learns about an old tradition, he persuades her to try and reignite the Christmas magic that brought neighboring communities together.

programme.title: Mystery on Mistletoe Lane
